Northam Platinum Says Its Full-Year Profit Declined by 46% to $49 Million

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-18T06:03:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-18/northam-platinum-says-its-full-year-profit-declined-by-46-to-49-million.html
Northam Platinum Ltd. (NHM)  said net
income for the 12 months to June 30 declined to 349.2 million
rand from 641 million rand a year earlier.  The company commented in a stock exchange statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  